lyrics:
(Verse 1)
Fireflies dance in the summer air
Heartbeat slows, worries don't compare
Stars peek through the twilight haze
Love whispers promises in a sweet, melodious daze

(Chorus)
Small town dreams, hearts beat as one
Two souls entwined, beneath the setting sun
Hope blooms bright, like wildflowers in the field
In this haven of love, our future is revealed
